# Frontend production env vars. Copy this into your hosting provider's
# environment variables panel (Vercel → Settings → Environment Variables).
#
# Leave VITE_API_URL unset to fall back to bundled JSON (~5,343 courses).
# Set it to the public origin of your API to enable /search, /api/careers,
# /api/funding, /api/insights, /api/fx and currency conversion.

# VITE_API_URL=https://mcm-api.fly.dev
